Must have MAX_PROB_VAR build >=9

Tests following features:
Phase Field 1 operability
Level set operability
coupled phase field and level set operability
1-way coupling for overset grid capability
Couple overset grid and level-set free surface coupling

Benchmark output file in benchmark.txt
generated with -se and -so.    Make sure you are comparing apples to apples

Runs 10 time steps. 

Takes about 0.36 min to run

